<title>
"Swimming in a Sea of Shame: Incorporating Emotions into Explanations o" by W. E. Douglas Creed, Bryant Ahsley Hudson et al.
</title>


<!-- FILE article_meta-tags.inc --><!-- FILE: /srv/sequoia/main/data/assets/site/article_meta-tags.inc -->
<meta itemprop="name" content="Swimming in a Sea of Shame: Incorporating Emotions into Explanations of Institutional Reproduction and Change">
<meta property="og:title" content="Swimming in a Sea of Shame: Incorporating Emotions into Explanations of Institutional Reproduction and Change">
